* Integrating Bootstrap with Rails
1. Add the bootstrap and autoprefixer-rails gem to Gemfile.
2. bundle install

* Import Bootstrap CSS assets
3. Rename the app/assets/stylesheets/application.css to application.css.sass
4. Add the following two lines to that application.css.sass file
@import "bootstrap-sprockets"
@import "bootstrap"

* Import Bootstrap javascript assets
4. Add the following line to app/assets/javascripts/application.js file after "//= require jquery"

//= require bootstrap-sprockets
